ndoa tovuti hii kutoka kwenye nyaraka %s.','The requested site does not exist.'=>'Tovuti iliyoitishwa haipatikani.','Path'=>'Njia','Domain'=>'domein','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Users_Screen">Documentation on Network Users</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Users_Screen">Nyaraka kuhusu Watumizi wa Mtandao</a>','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Themes_Screen">Documentation on Network Themes</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Themes_Screen">Nyaraka kuhusu Mandari ya Mtandao</a>','Warning! Problem updating %1$s. Your server may not be able to connect to sites running on it. Error message: %2$s'=>'Onyo! Shida kusasisha %1$s. Seva yako inaweza kuwa na uwezo wa kuungana na tovuti zinazoendesha juu yake. Ujumbe wa hitilafu: %2$s','%s theme deleted.'=>'%s dhima imefutwa.' . "\0" . '%s dhima yamefutwa.','%s theme disabled.'=>'mandhari %s yamezimwa.' . "\0" . 'mandhari %s yamezimwa','%s theme enabled.'=>'%s dhima imewezeshwa.' . "\0" . '%s dhima yamewezeshwa.','Yes, delete these themes'=>'Ndio, futa dhima haya','You are about to remove the following themes:'=>'Unakaribia kuondoa tovuti zifuatazo:','These themes may be active on other sites in the network.'=>'Dhima haya yanaweza kuwa amilifu kwenye tovuti zingine kwenye mtandao huu.','Delete Themes'=>'Futa dhima','Size in kilobytes'=>'Ukubwa katika kilobytes','Allowed file types. Separate types by spaces.'=>'Aina za faili zinazoruhusiwa. Tenganisha aina na nafasi.','Add the following to your %1$s file in %2$s, <strong>replacing</strong> other WordPress rules:'=>'Ongeza yafuatayo kwa faili yako ya %1$s katika %2$s, <strong> urekebishaji</strong> zingine za WordPress:','Confirm your action'=>'Hakikisha kitendo hiki','Hover over any user on the list to make the edit links appear. The Edit link on the left will take you to their Edit User profile page; the Edit link on the right by any site name goes to an Edit Site screen for that site.'=>'Tembea juu ya mtumizi yeyote kwenye orodha ili kufanya viungo vya kihariri ionekane. Kiunga cha Hariri upande wa kushoto kitakupeleka kwenye ukurasa wao wa wasifu wa Hariri; kiunga cha Hariri upande wa kulia na jina lolote la tovuti huenda kwenye skrini ya Tovuti ya Hariri ya tovuti hiyo.','To search for a site, <strong>enter the path or domain</strong>.'=>'Kutafuta tovuti, <strong> weka njia au kikoa</strong>.','To search for a user, <strong>enter an email address or username</strong>. Use a wildcard to search for a partial username, such as user&#42;.'=>'Kutafuta mtumizi, <strong> ingiza anwani ya barua pepe au jina la mtumizi </strong>. Tumia kadi ya mwituni kutafuta jina la mtumizi la sehemu, kama vile mtumiaji&#42;.','To add a new site, <strong>click Create a New Site</strong>.'=>'Kuongeza tovuti mpya, <strong>bofya Huluku Tovuti Mpya</strong>.','To add a new user, <strong>click Create a New User</strong>.'=>'Kuongeza mtumiaji mpya, <strong>bofya Huluku Mtumiaji Mpya</strong>.','Quick Tasks'=>'Kazi za haraka','To search for a user or site, use the search boxes.'=>'Kutafuta mtumiaji au wavuti, tumia masanduku ya utafutaji.','The Right Now widget on this screen provides current user and site counts on your network.'=>'Widget Sasa hivi kwenye skrini hii hutoa hesabu za watumizi wa sasa na wavuti kwenye mtandao wako.','Modify global network settings'=>'Badili mipangilio jumla ya mtandao','Update your network'=>'Sasisha mtandao wako','Install and activate themes or plugins'=>'Sakinisha na uamlishe dhima au vidude','Add and manage sites or users'=>'Ongeza au umeneji tovuti au watumiaji','From here you can:'=>'Kutoka hapa unaweza:','Welcome to your Network Admin. This area of the Administration Screens is used for managing all aspects of your Multisite Network.'=>'Karibu kwa Msimamizi wa Mtandao wako. Sehemu hii ya skrini za Utawala inatumika kwa kusimamia huduma zote za Mtandao wako wa Multisite.','Only use this screen once you have updated to a new version of WordPress through Updates/Available Updates (via the Network Administration navigation menu or the Toolbar). Clicking the Upgrade Network button will step through each site in the network, five at a time, and make sure any database updates are applied.'=>'Tumia skrini hii mara tu utakaposasisha kwa toleo jipya la WordPress kupitia visasisho / Sasisho zinazopatikana (kupitia menyu ya Usimamizi wa Urambazaji wa Mtandao au Zana ya Zana). Kubofya kitufe cha Mtandao wa Kuboresha kunapitia kila tovuti kwenye mtandao, tano kwa wakati mmoja, na hakikisha sasisho zozote za hifadhidata zinatumika.','Upgrade Network'=>'Sasisha mtandao','Subdirectory networks may not be fully compatible with custom wp-content directories.'=>'Subdirectory networks may not be fully compatible with custom wp-content directories.','Add the designated lines of code to wp-config.php (just before <code>/*...stop editing...*/</code>) and <code>.htaccess</code> (replacing the existing WordPress rules).'=>'Add the designated lines of code to wp-config.php (just before <code>/*...stop editing...*/</code>) and <code>.htaccess</code> (replacing the existing WordPress rules).','Language Settings'=>'Mipangilio ya lugha','Super admins can no longer be added on the Options screen. You must now go to the list of existing users on Network Admin > Users and click on Username or the Edit action link below that name. This goes to an Edit User page where you can check a box to grant super admin privileges.'=>'Wasimamizi wakuu hawawezi kuongezwa tena kwenye Skrini ya Chaguzi. Lazima sasa uende kwenye orodha ya watumizi waliopo kwenye Usimamizi wa Mtandao> Watumizi na ubonyeze jina la mtumizi au kiunga cha kihariri cha hatua chini ya jina hilo. Hii inakwenda kwenye ukurasa wa Kuhariri Mtumizi ambapo unaweza kuangalia sanduku ili umpe mamlaka ya msimamizi mkuu.','Enter the username and email.'=>'Weka jina la utumizi ama anwani ya barua pepe.','User created.'=>'Mtumiaji amehulukiwa.','Select a user to remove.'=>'Chagua mtumiaji wa kuondolewa.','Select a user to change role.'=>'Chagua mtumiaji wa kubadilishwa majukumu.','Enter the username of an existing user.'=>'Weka jina la mtumizi aliyeko.','User is already a member of this site.'=>'Mtumiaji tayari ni mwanachama wa tovuti.','Site options updated.'=>'Chaguo za tovuti zimewezeshwa.','Site added. <a href="%1$s">Visit Dashboard</a> or <a href="%2$s">Edit Site</a>'=>'Tovuti imeongezwa. <a href="%1$s">Tembelea Deshbodi</a> or <a href="%2$s">Hariri Tovuti</a>','This screen is for Super Admins to add new sites to the network. This is not affected by the registration settings.'=>'Skrini hii ni ya Wasimamizi Wakuu kuongeza tovuti mpya kwenye mtandao. Hii haiathiriwi na mipangilio ya usajili.','Site info updated.'=>'Maelezo ya tovuti imesasishwa.','You cannot delete a theme while it is active on the main site.'=>'Huwezi kufuta dhima ikiwa amilifu kwenye tovuti kuu.','Themes can be enabled on a site by site basis by the network admin on the Edit Site screen (which has a Themes tab); get there via the Edit action link on the All Sites screen. Only network admins are able to install or edit themes.'=>'Themes can be enabled on a site by site basis by the network admin on the Edit Site screen (which has a Themes tab); get there via the Edit action link on the All Sites screen. Only network admins are able to install or edit themes.','No, return me to the theme list'=>'La, nirudishe kwenye orodha ya dhima','Yes, delete this theme'=>'Ndio, futa dhima hii','Are you sure you want to delete these themes?'=>'Una hakika unataka kufuta mionekano hii?','You are about to remove the following theme:'=>'Unakaribia kuondoa dhima hii:','This theme may be active on other sites in the network.'=>'Hii dhima inaweza kuwa amilifu kwenye mtandao mwingine.','Delete Theme'=>'Futa dhima','Network enabled themes are not shown on this screen.'=>'MIonekano iliyowezeshwa kwa mtandao haionyeshwi kwenye skrini hii.','No theme selected.'=>'Dhima haijachaguliwa','Theme disabled.'=>'Mionekano imezimwa.','Theme enabled.'=>'Dhima imewezeshwa.','Edit Site: %s'=>'Hariri tovuti: %s','Invalid site ID.'=>'Kitambulisho batili cha tovuti.','Sorry, you are not allowed to delete the site %s.'=>'Samahani, hauruhusiwi kufuta tovuti %s.','Dashboard leads to the Dashboard for that site.'=>'Deshibodi litakuelekeza kwenye deshibodi ya tovuti hiyo.','An Edit link to a separate Edit Site screen.'=>'Kiungo cha uhariri kwenye skrini ya uhariri wa tovuti tofauti.','Cannot add user.'=>'Haiwezi kuongeza mtumiaji','Add User will set up a new user account on the network and send that person an email with username and password.'=>'Ongeza Mtumizi itaweka akaunti mpya ya mtumizi kwenye mtandao na kumtumia mtu huyo barua pepe na jina la mtumizi na nenosiri.','Updates'=>'Sasisho','Network Settings'=>'Mipangilio ya mtandao','Installed Themes'=>'Dhima zilizoakinishwa','All Sites'=>'Tovuti zote','Once you complete these steps, your network is enabled and configured. You will have to log in again.'=>'Ukimaliza hatua hizi, mtandao waako utakuwa umewezeshwa na kusanidiwa. Utalazimika kuingia tena.','To make your installation more secure, you should also add:'=>'Kufanya usanidi wako uwe salama, unafaa pia uongeze:','Complete the following steps to enable the features for creating a network of sites.'=>'Kamilisha hatua zifuatazo ili kuwezesha huduma za kuunda mtandao wa tovuti.','Enabling the Network'=>'Inawezesha mtandao','Please complete the configuration steps. To create a new network, you will need to empty or remove the network database tables.'=>'Tafadhali maliza hatua za kusanidi. Ili kuhuluku mtandao mpya, itabidi uage ama uondoe jedwali za hifadhidata za mtandao.','An existing WordPress network was detected.'=>'Mtandao uliopo wa WordPress uligunduliwa.','The original configuration steps are shown here for reference.'=>'Hatua za usanidi asili zinaonyeshwa hapa kwa kumbukumbu.','Your email address.'=>'Anwani yako ya barua pepe.','What would you like to call your network?'=>'Ungependa kuiitaje mtandao wako?','Network Title'=>'Kichwa cha mtandao','Because your installation is not new, the sites in your WordPress network must use sub-domains.'=>'Kwa sababu usanikishaji wako sio mpya, tovuti kwenye mtandao wako wa WordPress lazima zitumie kikoa kidogo.','Because your installation is in a directory, the sites in your WordPress network must use sub-directories.'=>'Kwa sababu usanikishaji wako uko kwenye saraka, tovuti kwenye mtandao wako wa WordPress lazima zitumie saraka-ndogo.','The main site in a sub-directory installation will need to use a modified permalink structure, potentially breaking existing links.'=>'Tovuti kuu katika usanidi wa saraka ndogo itahitaji kutumia muundo wa viungodumu uliobadilishwa, uwezekano wa kuvunja viungo vilivyopo.','Network Details'=>'Maelezo kuhusu mtandao','Server Address'=>'Anwani ya Seva','subdirectory exampleslike <code>%1$s/site1</code> and <code>%1$s/site2</code>'=>'like <code>%1$s/site1</code> and <code>%1$s/site2</code>','Sub-directories'=>'Saraka-ndogo','subdomain exampleslike <code>site1.%1$s</code> and <code>site2.%1$s</code>'=>'kama <code>site1.%1$s</code> na <code>site2.%1$s</code>','Sub-domains'=>'Domains ndogo','You will need a wildcard DNS record if you are going to use the virtual host (sub-domain) functionality.'=>'Utahitaji rekodi ya DNS ya kadi ya mwitu ikiwa utatumia utendaji wa mwenyeji wa kawaida (kikoa kidogo).','Addresses of Sites in your Network'=>'Anwani za Tovuti katika Mtandao wako','Fill in the information below and you&#8217;ll be on your way to creating a network of WordPress sites. Configuration files will be created in the next step.'=>'Jaza habari hapa chini na utakuwa kwenye njia yako ya kuunda mtandao wa tovuti za WordPress. Tutaunda faili za usanidi katika hatua inayofuata.','Welcome to the Network installation process!'=>'Karibu katika mchakato wa usanikishaji wa Mtandao!','Once the network is created, you may reactivate your plugins.'=>'Baada ya kuhuluku mtandao, unaweza kuwezesha vidude vyako tena.','Please <a href="%s">deactivate your plugins</a> before enabling the Network feature.'=>'Tafadhali <a href="%s">zima vijalizi vyako</a> kabla ya kuwezesha kipengee cha Mtandao.','Network'=>'Mtandao','The choice of subdirectory sites is disabled if this setup is more than a month old because of permalink problems with &#8220;/blog/&#8221; from the main site. This disabling will be addressed in a future version.'=>'Chaguo la tovuti zinazoongoza zinalemazwa ikiwa usanidi huu ni zaidi ya mwezi mmoja kwa sababu ya shida za vibali na &#8220;/blog/&#8221; kutoka tovuti kuu. kulemaza huku kutashughulikiwa katika toleo la baadaye.','Once you add this code and refresh your browser, multisite should be enabled. This screen, now in the Network Admin navigation menu, will keep an archive of the added code. You can toggle between Network Admin and Site Admin by clicking on the Network Admin or an individual site name under the My Sites dropdown in the Toolbar.'=>'Mara tu unapoongeza msimbo huu na kuburudisha kivinjari chako, multisite inapaswa kuwezeshwa. Skrini hii, ambayo sasa iko kwenye menyu ya Usimamizi wa Mtandao, itatunza kumbukumbu ya nambari iliyoongezwa. Unaweza kubadilisha kati ya Usimamizi wa Mtandao na Usimamizi wa Tovuti kwa kubonyeza Usimamizi wa Mtandao au jina la tovuti ya mtu chini ya kushuka kwa Tovuti Zangu kwenye Toolbar.','The next screen for Network Setup will give you individually-generated lines of code to add to your wp-config.php and .htaccess files. Make sure the settings of your FTP client make files starting with a dot visible, so that you can find .htaccess; you may have to create this file if it really is not there. Make backup copies of those two files.'=>'The next screen for Network Setup will give you individually-generated lines of code to add to your wp-config.php and .htaccess files. Make sure the settings of your FTP client make files starting with a dot visible, so that you can find .htaccess; you may have to create this file if it really is not there. Make backup copies of those two files.','Choose subdomains or subdirectories; this can only be switched afterwards by reconfiguring your installation. Fill out the network details, and click Install. If this does not work, you may have to add a wildcard DNS record (for subdomains) or change to another setting in Permalinks (for subdirectories).'=>'Choose subdomains or subdirectories; this can only be switched afterwards by reconfiguring your installation. Fill out the network details, and click Install. If this does not work, you may have to add a wildcard DNS record (for subdomains) or change to another setting in Permalinks (for subdirectories).','This screen allows you to configure a network as having subdomains (<code>site1.example.com</code>) or subdirectories (<code>example.com/site1</code>). Subdomains require wildcard subdomains to be enabled in Apache and DNS records, if your host allows it.'=>'This screen allows you to configure a network as having subdomains (<code>site1.example.com</code>) or subdirectories (<code>example.com/site1</code>). Subdomains require wildcard subdomains to be enabled in Apache and DNS records, if your host allows it.','Create a Network of WordPress Sites'=>'Huluku mtandao kwa wavuti zako za WordPress','The Network creation panel is not for WordPress MU networks.'=>'The Network creation panel is not for WordPress MU networks.','Warning! User cannot be modified. The user %s is a network administrator.'=>'Onyo! Mtumizi hawezi kuhaririwa. Mtumizi %s ni msimamizi wa mtandao','If the admin email for the new site does not exist in the database, a new user will also be created.'=>'If the admin email for the new site does not exist in the database, a new user will also be created.','Hovering over each site reveals seven options (three for the primary site):'=>'Hovering over each site reveals seven options (three for the primary site):','Operational settings has fields for the network&#8217;s name and admin email.'=>'Operational settings has fields for the network&#8217;s name and admin email.','The bulk action will permanently delete selected users, or mark/unmark those selected as spam. Spam users will have posts removed and will be unable to sign up again with the same email addresses.'=>'The bulk action will permanently delete selected users, or mark/unmark those selected as spam. Spam users will have posts removed and will be unable to sign up again with the same email addresses.','You can also go to the user&#8217;s profile page by clicking on the individual username.'=>'You can also go to the user&#8217;s profile page by clicking on the individual username.','Upload settings control the size of the uploaded files and the amount of available upload space for each site. You can change the default value for specific sites when you edit a particular site. Allowed file types are also listed (space separated only).'=>'Upload settings control the size of the uploaded files and the amount of available upload space for each site. You can change the default value for specific sites when you edit a particular site. Allowed file types are also listed (space separated only).','You can make an existing user an additional super admin by going to the Edit User profile page and checking the box to grant that privilege.'=>'Unaweza kufanya mtumizi aliyepo kuwa msimamizi bora zaidi kwa kwenda kwenye ukurasa wa Kuhariri Wasifu na angalia kisanduku ili upewe fursa hiyo.','Users who are signed up to the network without a site are added as subscribers to the main or primary dashboard site, giving them profile pages to manage their accounts. These users will only see Dashboard and My Sites in the main navigation until a site is created for them.'=>'Users who are signed up to the network without a site are added as subscribers to the main or primary dashboard site, giving them profile pages to manage their accounts. These users will only see Dashboard and My Sites in the main navigation until a site is created for them.','You can sort the table by clicking on any of the table headings and switch between list and excerpt views by using the icons above the users list.'=>'You can sort the table by clicking on any of the table headings and switch between list and excerpt views by using the icons above the users list.','This table shows all users across the network and the sites to which they are assigned.'=>'Jedwali hili linaonyesha watumizi wote kwenye mtandao na wavuti waliopewa.','If this process fails for any reason, users logging in to their sites will force the same update.'=>'If this process fails for any reason, users logging in to their sites will force the same update.','If a version update to core has not happened, clicking this button will not affect anything.'=>'Ikiwa sasisho la toleo la msingi halijafanyika, kubofya kitufe hiki hakutaathiri chochote.','If the network admin disables a theme that is in use, it can still remain selected on that site. If another theme is chosen, the disabled theme will not appear in the site&#8217;s Appearance > Themes screen.'=>'Ikiwa msimamizi wa mtandao atalemaza mwonekano ambaoo unatumika, bado unaweza kubaki kuchaguliwa kwenye tovuti hiyo. Ikiwa mwonekano mwingine umechaguliwa, mwonekano uliolemazwa hautaonekana kwenye Mwonekano wa tovuti > skirini ya Mwonekano.','This screen enables and disables the inclusion of themes available to choose in the Appearance menu for each site. It does not activate or deactivate which theme a site is currently using.'=>'This screen enables and disables the inclusion of themes available to choose in the Appearance menu for each site. It does not activate or deactivate which theme a site is currently using.','This is the main table of all sites on this network. Switch between list and excerpt views by using the icons above the right side of the table.'=>'This is the main table of all sites on this network. Switch between list and excerpt views by using the icons above the right side of the table.','Menu setting enables/disables the plugin menus from appearing for non super admins, so that only super admins, not site admins, have access to activate plugins.'=>'Menu setting enables/disables the plugin menus from appearing for non super admins, so that only super admins, not site admins, have access to activate plugins.','New site settings are defaults applied when a new site is created in the network. These include welcome email for when a new site or user account is registered, and what&#8127;s put in the first post, page, comment, comment author, and comment URL.'=>'New site settings are defaults applied when a new site is created in the network. These include welcome email for when a new site or user account is registered, and what&#8127;s put in the first post, page, comment, comment author, and comment URL.','Registration settings can disable/enable public signups. If you let others sign up for a site, install spam plugins. Spaces, not commas, should separate names banned as sites for this network.'=>'Registration settings can disable/enable public signups. If you let others sign up for a site, install spam plugins. Spaces, not commas, should separate names banned as sites for this network.','This screen sets and changes options for the network as a whole. The first site is the main site in the network and network options are pulled from that original site&#8217;s options.'=>'This screen sets and changes options for the network as a whole. The first site is the main site in the network and network options are pulled from that original site&#8217;s options.','The following words are reserved for use by WordPress functions and cannot be used as site names: %s'=>'Maneno yafuatayo yamehifadhiwa kwa matumizi ya kazi za WordPress na hayawezi kutumiwa kama majina ya tovuti: %s','If your browser does not start loading the next page automatically, click this link:'=>'If your browser doesn&#8217;t start loading the next page automatically, click this link:','If you want to ban domains from site registrations. One domain per line.'=>'Ikiwa unataka kupiga marufuku vikoa kutoka kwa usajili wa tovuti. Kikoa kimoja kwa kila mstari.','If you want to limit site registrations to certain domains. One domain per line.'=>'Ikiwa unataka kupunguza usajili wa tovuti kwa vikoa fulani. Kikoa kimoja kwa kila mstari.','Users removed from spam.'=>'Watumiaji wametolewa kutoka kwa barua taka.','Site marked as spam.'=>'Tovuti imetambuliwa kuwa haramu.','Site removed from spam.'=>'Tovuti imetolewa kutoka kwa barua taka.','Sites marked as spam.'=>'Tovuti zimetambuliwa kuwa haramu.','Sites removed from spam.'=>'Wavuti zimetolewa kutoka kwa barua taka.','Users deleted.'=>'Watumiaji wamefutwa.','Users marked as spam.'=>'Watumizi wametambuliwa kuwa haramu.','Site unarchived.'=>'Tovuti imetolewa kutokwa kwaa nyaraka.','Site archived.'=>'Tovuti imehifadhiwa kwenye barua taka.','Sorry, you are not allowed to change the current site.'=>'Samahani, huruhusiwi kubadilisha tovuti hii.','There was an error creating the user.'=>'Kumekuwa na kosa kwenye kuhuluku mtumiaji mpya.','Upload file types'=>'Pakia aina ya faili','Limit total size of files uploaded to %s MB'=>'Punguza ukubwa wa faili zilizopakiwa kwa MB %s','The URL for the first comment on a new site.'=>'Anwani ya maoni ya kwanza kwenye tovuti.','The author of the first comment on a new site.'=>'Mwandishi wa maoni ya kwanza kwenye tovuti mpya.','The first comment on a new site.'=>'Maoni ya kwanza kwenye tovuti mpya.','The first page on a new site.'=>'Ukurasa wa kwanza kwenye tovuti mpya','The first post on a new site.'=>'Chapisho la kwanza kwenye tovuti mpya.','All done!'=>'Yote yamekamilika!','Both sites and user accounts can be registered'=>'Akaunti za tovuti na za watumizi zinaweza kusajiliwa.','Logged in users may register new sites'=>'Watumizi walioingia wanaweza kusajili tovuti mpya.','User accounts may be registered'=>'Akaunti za watumizi zinaweza kusajiliwa','Registration is disabled'=>'Usajili hauruhusiwi.','Enable administration menus'=>'Wezesha menyu za wasimamizi','Upload Settings'=>'Pakia mipangilio','New Site Settings'=>'Mipangilio ya tovuti mpya','Registration Settings'=>'Mipangilio ya usajili','Operational Settings'=>'Mipangilio ya Kufanya Kazi','Missing email address.'=>'Anwani za barua pepe zisizopo','Missing or invalid site address.'=>'Anwani ya tovuti haiko au ni batili.','Next Sites'=>'Tovuti Mpya','Site upload space'=>'Nafasi ya kupakia ya tovuti','The welcome email sent to new site owners.'=>'Barua pepe ya kuwalaki wamiliki wapya ya wavuti.','Users are not allowed to register these sites. Separate names by spaces.'=>'Watumizi hawaruhusiwi kusajili tovuti hizi. Tenganisha majina kwa nafasi.','Send the network admin an email notification every time someone registers a site or user account'=>'Tumia msimamizi wa mtandao arifu ya barua pepe kila wakati mtu anasajili tovuti au akaunti ya mtumizi','Network Admin Email'=>'Barua pepe ya msimamizi mtandao','A new user will be created if the above email address is not in the database.'=>'Mtumiajji mpya atahulukiwa iwapo anwani hii ya barua pepe haitakuwepo kwenye hifadhidata.','Admin Email'=>'Barua pepe ya Msimamizi','Add Site'=>'Ongeza tovuti','Default Language'=>'Lugha msingi','Max upload file size'=>'Ukubwa wa faili wa juu','First Comment URL'=>'Anwani ya maoni ya kwanza','First Comment Author'=>'Mwandishi wa maoni ya kwanza','First Comment'=>'Maoni ya kwanza','First Page'=>'Ukurasa wa kwanza','The welcome email sent to new users.'=>'Barua pepe ya karibisho wametumiwa watumizi wote wapya','Welcome User Email'=>'Barua pepe ya kumkaribisha mtumiaji','Welcome Email'=>'Barua pepe ya kukaribisha','Banned Email Domains'=>'Domains za barua pepe zilizopigwa marufuku','Limited Email Registrations'=>'Usajili wa Barua Pepe Umesitishwa','Banned Names'=>'Majina yaliyopigwa marufuku','Registration notification'=>'Taarifa ya usajili','Allow new registrations'=>'Kubali usajili upya','Duplicated username or email address.'=>'Umerudia ina la mtumizi au barua pepe','Cannot create an empty user.'=>'Huwezi kuongeza mtumizi bure','Confirm'=>'Hakikisha']];